OL,3,CFormer British soldier pays tribute to
OL,4,CManx man volunteer who died in Ukraine
OL,6,FA former British army soldier has paid
OL,7,Ftribute to the late Chris Garrett, the
OL,8,FManx man who lost his life
OL,9,Fvolunteering in Ukraine.
OL,11,FShaun Pinner described Chris as 'a
OL,12,Fcharismatic man, deeply thoughtful,
OL,13,Fwho loved his family'.
OL,15,FChris, fondly known as 'Swampy', was
OL,16,Fborn on the Isle of Man, and raised in
OL,17,Fthe seaside town of Peel on the west
OL,18,Fcoast.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
