FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772651488
OL,3,CFormer British soldier pays tribute to
OL,4,CManx man volunteer who died in Ukraine
OL,6,FHe had been volunteering in Ukraine
OL,7,Fsince 2014, working to clear landmines
OL,8,Fas a bomb disposal expert.
OL,10,FFollowing the Russian invasion, Chris
OL,11,Fstayed to help train troops fighting
OL,12,Fin the country, volunteering with the
OL,13,FUkraine National Guard.
OL,15,FThe 40-year-old was killed on 6 May
OL,16,F2025, during an incident near Izyum in
OL,17,Fthe east of Ukraine.
OL,19,FShaun became friends with Chris during
OL,20,Ftheir time together in Ukraine.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772651488
OL,3,CFormer British soldier pays tribute to
OL,4,CManx man volunteer who died in Ukraine
OL,6,FShaun moved to the country with his
OL,7,FUkrainian wife, before joining their
OL,8,Farmed forces in 2018, but was captured
OL,9,Fby Russian forces during the siege of
OL,10,FMariupol in April 2022.
OL,12,FHe was freed in September 2022, after
OL,13,Fa gruelling five months inside a
OL,14,FRussian prison where he was subject to
OL,15,Ftorture, a stabbing, and starvation.
OL,17,FDespite this, he said it was 'the best
OL,18,Fdecision I've ever made', adding that
OL,19,Fit was Chris who convinced him to stay.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772651488
OL,3,CFormer British soldier pays tribute to
OL,4,CManx man volunteer who died in Ukraine
OL,6,F"I just brought nine years military
OL,7,Fexperience which Chris found
OL,8,Fvaluable... in light of everything
OL,9,Fthat went on, it was still the best
OL,10,Fdecision I've ever made.
OL,12,F"His knowledge of the area and mines
OL,13,Fwas invaluable, so he was teaching the
OL,14,Fpolice, the military.
OL,16,F"I mean there's a big Isle of Man flag
OL,17,Fnow in the centre of Maidan, and
OL,18,Fpeople know where the Isle of Man is,
OL,19,Fand Chris was a part of that -
OL,20,Feverybody knew him from the northern
OL,21,Fpart of Ukraine to the Azov Sea."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772651488
OL,3,CFormer British soldier pays tribute to
OL,4,CManx man volunteer who died in Ukraine
OL,6,FWhile in Ukraine, Chris met his
OL,7,Fpartner Courtney Pollock - a paramedic
OL,8,Fworking in Ukraine from the United
OL,9,FStates.
OL,11,FIt was here where she met 'Swampy',
OL,12,Fbefore falling pregnant with their
OL,13,Fdaughter Reed.
OL,15,FThe two-year-old is now settling into
OL,16,Fisland life, alongside Courtney and
OL,17,FChris' family.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772651488
OL,3,CFormer British soldier pays tribute to
OL,4,CManx man volunteer who died in Ukraine
OL,6,FCourtney said: "She's what keeps me
OL,7,Fgoing every day. She's been able to
OL,8,Fsettle really well here, and being
OL,9,Faround Chris' family has been really
OL,10,Fgood. Obviously not being here with
OL,11,FChris, and doing it all with him just
OL,12,Fadds levels of complexity. It's
OL,13,Fbeautiful, and it's healing, and I am
OL,14,Fthankful for what the Isle of Man has
OL,15,Fbeen to us."
OL,17,FShe added: "He would have had a blast
OL,18,Fwith her right now, and he would have
OL,19,Fbeen so good, and I think that's what
OL,20,Fis the hardest."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772651488
OL,3,CFormer British soldier pays tribute to
OL,4,CManx man volunteer who died in Ukraine
OL,6,FWhile in Ukraine, Chris and Courtney
OL,7,Falso co-founded a humanitarian charity
OL,8,Fcalled 'Prevail Together' - a group
OL,9,Fproviding 'essential assistance' to
OL,10,FUkraine.
OL,12,FShaun is also an ambassador of the
OL,13,Fcharity, helping to raise awareness of
OL,14,Fthe work in Chris' honour.
OL,16,FShaun was one of the first people to
OL,17,Flearn of Chris' death, describing it
OL,18,Fas 'difficult to deal with'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772651488
OL,3,CFormer British soldier pays tribute to
OL,4,CManx man volunteer who died in Ukraine
OL,6,FHe said: "It was unexpected. It was
OL,7,Fjust a call in the afternoon from a
OL,8,Ffriend said 'there's been an
OL,9,Faccident', and I had to break it to to
OL,10,FCourtney. I mean, it was the one thing
OL,11,FI don't ever want to do again. It's
OL,12,Fexceptionally hard.
OL,14,F"I've lost so many friends in Ukraine,
OL,15,Fyou know, in my wedding pictures, 60%
OL,16,Fof those are either killed or in
OL,17,Fcaptivity - it's a tragedy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1772651488
OL,3,CFormer British soldier pays tribute to
OL,4,CManx man volunteer who died in Ukraine
OL,6,FIt doesn't get any easier, you just
OL,7,Fget better at dealing with stuff like
OL,8,Fthat because, you know, you've gone
OL,9,Fthrough so many friends now and lost
OL,10,Fso many friends, you just have to keep
OL,11,Fmoving forward.
OL,13,F"So I don't think any of us are really
OL,14,Fprocessed it yet, and when the war
OL,15,Ffinishes, then maybe you will start to
OL,16,Fremember all those people that have
OL,17,Fmade the ultimate sacrifice, including
OL,18,FChris."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
